isagrees (by a value of the Bayes factor about $10^{-10}-10^{-11}$) with a\nhigher value of local motion which one can infer from the amplitude of the\ndipole signal obtained from the CatWISE2020 quasar catalog using the WISE and\nNEOWISE data set.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Jun 2021 18:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Nov 2021 07:20:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-19"}
