in the form\nof D) of ~2.4% previously estimated from the observed 4.4 $\\mu$m to 3.3 $\\mu$m\nband ratio based on the A$_{4.4}$/A$_{3.3}$ ratio of mono-deuterated PAHs is\nrobust.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jun 2021 04:58:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-04"}
