ate\nkernels, the cosmic web radio emission is clearly detectable by\ncross-correlation techniques and this signal is separable from the embedded\nextragalactic radio population. We offer the simulation as a public resource\ntowards the development of techniques for detecting and measuring the\nsynchrotron cosmic web.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jun 2021 06:30:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-27"}
